Packages 
Package Description
com
Provides the classes of game components used in this game
com.end
Provides the classes of ends elements
com.frogger
Provides the classes of frogger
com.obstacle
Provides the classes of obstacle elements kill frogger when it touches them
com.obstacle.car
Provides the class of cars extends from Obstacle class
com.obstacle.snake
Provides the class of snake extends from Obstacle class
com.obstacle.truck
Provides the classes of trucks extend from Obstacle class
com.platform
Provides the classes of platform elements help frogger cross the river
com.platform.crocodile
Provides the classes of crocodile parts extend from Platform class
com.platform.log
Provides the class of logs extends from Platform class
com.platform.turtle
Provides the classes of turtles extend from Platform class
controller
Provides the classes which could used to control FXML files (view)
controller.gameController
Provides the classes of controllers manipulate the game status
controller.helpPagesController
Provides the classes of controllers manipulate the help info pages
gameApp
Contains the Main extends from Application which could launch the entire game.
util
Provides the classes which could be used as kits which could be applied in other classes, including: 1.
